                            <comment id="52827" author="jhammond" created="Thu, 21 Feb 2013 14:21:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Oleg, can you suggest a reasonable upper limit on the amount of memory that the MDT allocate to serve a single HSM request?&lt;/p&gt;

